      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car being sold as a budget-friendly runaround or project for someone handy. It\u2019s not perfect and it shows its age, but it\u2019s an affordable way into a car without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re looking for cheap wheels, a parts donor, or something to tinker with, this could be a great fit. Priced to sell and worth a look for the right buyer.",
